Class Discount.DiscountID

java.lang.Object
CSC540.WolfWR.models.DomainObject
CSC540.WolfWR.models.Discount.DiscountID
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Enclosing class:
Discount
@Embeddable public static class Discount.DiscountID extends DomainObject
Represents the composite primary key for the Discount entity. This class is used to define the combination of productID and start as the primary key for the Discount table.
